.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/research.md:213:  D1 Routing/Activation   25   → interSkill 12 (advisor) + intraSkill 13 (smart router)
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/research.md:214:  D2 Unprompted Discovery 20   → Hit@k / Recall@k / MRR / cost-weighted precision
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/research.md:215:  D4 Usefulness (ablation)25   → skill-on − skill-off; net value = benefit − context cost
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/research.md:216:  D3 Efficiency           15   → calls/tokens to first expected resource; wasted loads
.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/001-skill-benchmark-deep-research/research/research.md:217:Gate layer (caps verdict regardless of weighted score):
