     9	 * same rate-limit / backoff / pause-sentinel machinery, but the invocation layer
    10	 * routes through an executor map keyed on `opts.executor` instead of being
    11	 * hardcoded to `opencode run`.
    12	 *
    13	 * Interface (matches the dispatcher seam):
    14	 *   dispatch({ prompt_file, executor, model, agent, variant, state_dir, mock, mock_mode, cwd, timeout_ms })
